ok i can help you with this, go onto your client, and log onto your server(using silab would be pretty helpful for this) and just put your mouse over the “jad” on the tab, on the top left of the screen it should say a number, something like 154, 166, something similar to that. then open your client.java and search for case [# from before] so it may be case 154: or case 166: and then look below it, it will say coords, just change them to the coords that you want them to tele you to [= hope this helped
